{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:1","prev_osis_id":"Isa.058.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les crimes du peuple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. \u00c9s 50:1-3. (Mi 3:1-4, 9, 10; 6:12, 13. J\u00e9 9:2-9.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Non, la main de l\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019est pas trop courte pour sauver,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ni son oreille trop dure pour entendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.58.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 58:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.58.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:2","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Mais ce sont vos crimes qui mettent une s\u00e9paration<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Entre vous et votre Dieu;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ce sont vos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s qui vous cachent sa face<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et l\u2019emp\u00eachent de vous \u00e9couter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:3","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Car vos mains sont souill\u00e9es de sang,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vos doigts de crimes;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Vos l\u00e8vres prof\u00e8rent le mensonge,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Votre langue fait entendre l\u2019iniquit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.2","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:2","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:4","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Nul ne se plaint avec justice,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nul ne plaide avec droiture;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils s\u2019appuient sur des choses vaines et disent des fausset\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Ils con\u00e7oivent le mal et enfantent le crime.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.3","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:3","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:5","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils couvent des \u0153ufs de basilic,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils tissent des toiles d\u2019araign\u00e9e.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui mange de leurs \u0153ufs meurt;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et, si l\u2019on en brise un, il sort une vip\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.4","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:4","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:6","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Leurs toiles ne servent point \u00e0 faire un v\u00eatement,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils ne peuvent se couvrir de leur ouvrage;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Leurs \u0153uvres sont des \u0153uvres d\u2019iniquit\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et les actes de violence sont dans leurs mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.5","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:5","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:7","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    Leurs pieds courent au mal,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils ont h\u00e2te de r\u00e9pandre le sang innocent;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Leurs pens\u00e9es sont des pens\u00e9es d\u2019iniquit\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le ravage et la ruine sont sur leur route.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.6","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:6","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:8","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ils ne connaissent pas le chemin de la paix,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il n\u2019y a point de justice dans leurs voies;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils prennent des sentiers d\u00e9tourn\u00e9s:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quiconque y marche ne conna\u00eet point la paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.7","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:7","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:9","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-15: cf. (Mi 7:2-6. Esd 9:6, 7.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi l\u2019arr\u00eat de d\u00e9livrance est loin de nous,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et le salut ne nous atteint pas;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous attendons la lumi\u00e8re, et voici les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La clart\u00e9, et nous marchons dans l\u2019obscurit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.8","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:8","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:10","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Nous t\u00e2tonnons comme des aveugles le long d\u2019un mur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous t\u00e2tonnons comme ceux qui n\u2019ont point d\u2019yeux;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous chancelons \u00e0 midi comme de nuit,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Au milieu de l\u2019abondance nous ressemblons \u00e0 des morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.9","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:9","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:11","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Nous grondons tous comme des ours,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous g\u00e9missons comme des colombes;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous attendons la d\u00e9livrance, et elle n\u2019est pas l\u00e0,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le salut, et il est loin de nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.10","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:10","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:12","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Car nos transgressions sont nombreuses devant toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et nos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s t\u00e9moignent contre nous;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nos transgressions sont avec nous,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et nous connaissons nos crimes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.11","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:11","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:13","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 coupables et infid\u00e8les envers l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous avons abandonn\u00e9 notre Dieu;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous avons prof\u00e9r\u00e9 la violence et la r\u00e9volte,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Con\u00e7u et m\u00e9dit\u00e9 dans le c\u0153ur des paroles de mensonge;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.12","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:12","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:14","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et la d\u00e9livrance s\u2019est retir\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et le salut se tient \u00e9loign\u00e9;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 tr\u00e9buche sur la place publique,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la droiture ne peut approcher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.13","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:13","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:15","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>La v\u00e9rit\u00e9 a disparu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et celui qui s\u2019\u00e9loigne du mal est d\u00e9pouill\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-21: cf. (De 32:35-43. \u00c9s 63:1-6.) Ro 11:25-27.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019\u00c9ternel voit, d\u2019un regard indign\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019il n\u2019y a plus de droiture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.14","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:14","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:16","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Il voit qu\u2019il n\u2019y a pas un homme,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il s\u2019\u00e9tonne de ce que personne n\u2019interc\u00e8de;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Alors son bras lui vient en aide,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et sa justice lui sert d\u2019appui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.15","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:15","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:17","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>\n    Il se rev\u00eat de la justice comme d\u2019une cuirasse,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il met sur sa t\u00eate le casque du salut;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il prend la vengeance pour v\u00eatement,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il se couvre de la jalousie comme d\u2019un manteau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.18","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.16","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:16","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.18","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:18","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il rendra \u00e0 chacun selon ses \u0153uvres,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La fureur \u00e0 ses adversaires,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La pareille \u00e0 ses ennemis;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il rendra la pareille aux \u00eeles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.19","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.17","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:17","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.19","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:19","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>On craindra le nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel depuis l\u2019occident,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et sa gloire depuis le soleil levant;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quand l\u2019ennemi viendra comme un fleuve,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019esprit de l\u2019\u00c9ternel le mettra en fuite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.20","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.18","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:18","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.20","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:20","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.059.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>\n    Un r\u00e9dempteur viendra pour Sion,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour ceux de Jacob qui se convertiront de leurs p\u00e9ch\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.21","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.19","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:19","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.21","label":"","reference":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:21","prev_osis_id":"Isa.059.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Isa.060.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Isa.59.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Voici mon alliance avec eux, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mon esprit, qui repose sur toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et mes paroles, que j\u2019ai mises dans ta bouche,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne se retireront point de ta bouche, ni de la bouche de tes enfants,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ni de la bouche des enfants de tes enfants,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, d\u00e8s maintenant et \u00e0 jamais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Isa.59","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.60.1","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 60:1","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.60.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Isa.59.20","name":"\u00c9sa\u00efe 59:20","id":"fra-LSG:Isa.59.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc422e470.51861822');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc422e470.51861822\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc422e470.51861822","fums_js_i